<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.6.10">
<l>kōlaṅkoḷ cuvarkkamum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ kōlami ṉarakamum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ</l>
<l>kōlantikaḻ mōkkamum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ kōlaṅko ḷuyirkaḷum yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ</l>
<l>kōlaṅkoṭ ṭaṉimutal yāṉē yeṉṉuṅ kōlaṅkoṇ mukilvaṇṇa ṉēṟak kolō</l>
<l>kōlaṅko ḷulakat tīrkkeṉ collukēṉ kōlan tikaḻkō taiyeṉkūn talukkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>”I [am] beautiful heaven”, she says,</l>
	<l>“and I [am] beautiless hell”, she says,</l>
<l>“and I [am] liberation glittering with beauty”, she says,</l>
	<l>“and I [am] all the beautiful souls”, she says,</l>
<l>“I [am] the beautiful sole beginning”, she says,</l>
	<l>while the beautiful one with cloud colour settles in [her]?</l>
<l>What will I say to you of the beautiful world,</l>
	<l>about my [girl with] garlanded tresses glittering with beauty?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
